# Google Sans is Google's proprietary brand font — do NOT redistribute it from this
# public repo. Keep the .ttf files local; the built PDF embeds only a subset (fine).
# To build, place GoogleSans-{Regular,Medium,Bold,Italic}.ttf in fonts/.
fonts/GoogleSans-*.ttf

# Outfit (open look-alike, only used for an alternate build) — not needed here.
fonts/Outfit.ttf
